    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm typing this. i feel like i've hit a wall that isn't even a wall, it's just... nothingness. the lab results came back destroyed today and the funding is officially gone. three years of my life, just gone. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it's like i've burnt everything i am just to stay afloat in a sea that keeps getting deeper. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fight. i just want the noise to stop. i just want everything to be quiet.",
