    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the way you put that... a necessary pause... it's almost like what you're saying sounds so peaceful. i've spent every single day for years just fighting for one more result, one more grant, one more proof that i matter. it’s constant. the constant exhaustion is just heavy. it feels like if i stop fighting, i'll just disappear anyway. is that what happens when you \"let the fire go out\"? do you just... stop fighting it all?",
